xt-align:center; width:150px;\"|{{increase}}41.515\n|style=\"text-align:center; width:150px;\"|{{increase}}204\n|style=\"text-align:center; width:150px;\"|{{increase}}41.729\n|}\n|}\n\n==Ground transport==\nBy Car or taxi Corfu Airport is located 2.7&nbsp;km from the city of Corfu and takes about 10 minutes. Bus services are provided between the Airport and the city centre.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.astikoktelkerkyras.gr/frequently-asked-questions-weg-95540.html|title=Frequently Asked Questions|website=Astikoktelkerkyras.gr|accessdate=24 January 2019}}</ref>\n\n==See also==\n*[[Transport in Greece]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n{{Commons category-inline|Corfu International Airport}}\n* Official Corfu Airport web site: [https://www.cfu-airport.gr/en Corfu Airport - Homepage] English/Greek\n* Pictures from Corfu Airport: [http://www.jetphotos.ch/aviationphotos/search.php?type=airport&value=2647, from JetPhotos.ch]\n* {{WAD|LGKR}}\n\n{{Portalbar|Greece|Aviation}}\n{{Airports in Greece|state=collapsed}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Airports in Greece]]\n[[Category:Buildings and structures in Corfu]]\n[[Category:Ioannis Kapodistrias]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=September 2019}}\n{{Infobox airport\n| name = Corfu International Airport \"Ioannis Kapodistrias\"\n| nativename = ''\u039a\u03c1\u03b1\u03c4\u03b9\u03ba\u03cc\u03c2 \u0391\u03b5\u03c1\u03bf\u03bb\u03b9\u03bc\u03ad\u03bd\u03b1\u03c2 \u039a\u03ad\u03c1\u03ba\u03c5\u03c1\u03b1\u03c2''\n| nativename-a = ''\"\u0399\u03c9\u03ac\u03bd\u03bd\u03b7\u03c2 \u039a\u03b1\u03c0\u03bf\u03b4\u03af\u03c3\u03c4\u03c1\u03b9\u03b1\u03c2\"''\n| nativename-r = \n| image = File:Corfu Airport Fraport Logo.png\n| image-width = 250\n| IATA = CFU\n| ICAO = LGKR\n| type = Public\n| owner = Greek Government\n| operator = [[Fraport|Fraport Greece]]\n| city-served = [[Corfu]]\n| location = Garitsa, [[Corfu]]\n| focus_city = * [[Aegean Airlines]]\n* [[Ellinair]]\n* [[Ryanair]]\n| metric-elev 