burg_Gotha_165771801_1854_0042.tif?logicalDiv=jportal_jparticle_00483206 p. 26]</ref>\n* {{Flagcountry|Second French Empire}}: [[Legion of Honour]], Grand Cross\n* {{Flagicon|Greece|royal}} [[Kingdom of Greece|Greece]]: [[Order of the Redeemer]], Grand Cross\n* {{Flagcountry|Kingdom of Hanover}}: [[Order of St. George (Hanover)|Order of St. George]], Knight, ''1858''<ref name=\"Hannover1865\">{{cite book|author=Staat Hannover|title=Hof- und Staatshandbuch f\u00fcr das K\u00f6nigreich Hannover: 1865|url=https://archive.org/details/bub_gb_bAFTAAAAcAAJ|year=1865|publisher=Berenberg|page=[https://archive.org/details/bub_gb_bAFTAAAAcAAJ/page/n56 38]}}</ref>\n* {{Flagcountry|Kingdom of Hawaii}}: [[Royal Order of Kamehameha I (decoration)|Royal Order of Kamehameha I]], Grand Cross, ''1881''<ref>Kalakaua to his sister, 28 July 1881, quoted in Greer, Richard A. (editor, 1967) \"[https://evols.library.manoa.hawaii.edu/bitstream/10524/186/JL05085.pdf The Royal Tourist\u2014Kalakaua's Letters Home from Tokio to London]\", ''Hawaiian Journal of History'', vol. 5, p. 102</ref>\n* {{flagicon|Hesse}} [[Electorate of Hesse|Hesse-Kassel]]: [[Order of the Golden Lion]], Knight, ''29 January 1866''<ref>{{cite book|title=Kurf\u00fcrstlich Hessisches Hof- und Staatshandbuch: 1866|url=https://archive.org/details/bub_gb_8vVSAAAAcAAJ|year=1866|publisher=Waisenhaus}}</ref>\n* {{flagicon image|Flagge Gro\u00dfherzogtum Hessen ohne Wappen.svg}} [[Hesse and by Rhine]]: [[Ludwig Order]], Grand Cross, ''10 December 1865''<ref>''Hof- und Staats-Handbuch des Gro\u00dfherzogtum Hessen'' (1879), \"Gro\u00dfherzogliche Orden und Ehrenzeichen\" [https://archive.org/details/hofundstaatshan00gergoog/page/n36 p. 12]</ref>\n* {{Flagcountry|Empire of Japan}}: [[Order of the Chrysanthemum]], Collar\n* {{Flag|Liberia}}: [[Humane Order of African Redemption]], Grand Commander\n* {{Flag|Sovereign Military Order of Malta}}: Bailiff Grand Cross of Honour and Devotion<ref name=\"p19\">Justus Perthes, ''Almanach de Gotha'' (1909) [https://archive.org/details/almanachdegotha00unse_88/page/n53 p. 19]</ref>\n* {{Flagicon image|Flagge Gro\u00dfherzogt\u00fcmer Mecklenburg.svg}} [[Mecklenburg]]:\n** [[House Order of the Wendish Crown]], Grand Cross with Crown in Ore\n** [[Order of the Griffon (Mecklenburg)|Order of the Griffon]], Grand Cross\n* {{flagicon image|Flag of Mexico (1864-1867).svg}} [[Second Mexican Empire|Mexico]]: [[Mexican Imperial Orders#Order of the Mexican Eagle|Imperial Order of the Mexican Eagle]], Grand Cross\n* {{flag|Monaco}}: [[Order of Saint-Charles]], Grand Cross\n* {{flag|Netherlands}}: [[Order of the Netherlands Lion]], Grand Cross\n* {{Flag|Oldenburg}}: [[House and Merit Order of Peter Frederick Louis|House and Merit Order of Duke Peter Friedrich Ludwig]], Grand Cross with Golden Crown, ''1 August 1856''<ref name=\"Oldenburg1873\">{{cite book|author=Staat Oldenburg|title=Hof- und Staatshandbuch des Gro\u00dfherzogtums Oldenburg: f\u00fcr ... 1872/73|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=NpBYAAAAcAAJ&pg=PA30|year=1873|publisher=Schulze|page=30}}</ref>\n* {{Flag|Ottoman Empire}}:\n** [[Order of the Medjidie]], 1st Class\n** [[Order of Osmanieh]], 1st Class\n** Order of the Hanedan-i-Ali-Osman\n* {{flagicon image|Amir Kabir Flag.svg}} [[Qajar Iran|Persia]]:\n** [[Order of the Lion and the Sun]], Grand Cordon\n** Order of the August Portrait, ''16 June 1873''<ref>{{cite book|author=[[Naser al-Din Shah Qajar]]|translator=[[James Redhouse]] |title=The Diary of H.M. The Shah of Persia during his tour through Europe in A.D. 1873: A verbatim translation |date=1874 |publisher=John Murray |location=London |page=130 |chapter=Chapter III: Prussia, Germany, Belgium |chapter-url=https://archive.org/details/diaryofhmshahofp00nasiuoft/page/130 |isbn=}}</ref>\n* {{flagcountry|Kingdom of Portugal}}:<ref name=\"Agraciamentos\">{{cite journal|last1=Bragan\u00e7a |first1=Jose Vicente de|last2= |first2= |date=2014 |title=Agraciamentos Portugueses Aos Pr\u00edncipes da Casa Saxe-Coburgo-Gota |url=https://www.academia.edu/10576008/AGRACIAMENTOS_PORTUGUESES_AOS_PR%C3%8DNCIPES_DA_CASA_SAXE-COBURGO-GOTA_PORTUGUESE_HONOURS_AWARDED_TO_PRINCES_OF_THE_HOUSE_OF_SAXE-COBURG-GOTHA |language=portuguese|trans-title=Portuguese Honours awarded to Princes of the House of Saxe-Coburg and Gotha|journal=Pro Phalaris |volume=9-10 |issue= |pages=9-10 |doi= ||access-date=28 November 2019 }}</ref>\n** [[Order of the Tower and Sword]], Grand Cross, ''6 September 1853''\n** [[Sash of the Three Orders]], Grand Cross, ''8 January 1866''\n* {{flagicon image|Flag of the Kingdom of Prussia (1803-1892).svg}} [[Kingdom of Prussia|Prussia]]:\n** [[Order of the Black Eagle]], Knight\n** [[Order of the Red Eagle]], Grand Cross\n** Royal [[House Order of Hohenzollern]], Grand Commander\n* {{Flag|Qing dynasty}}: [[Order of the Double Dragon]], Class I Grade I\n* {{Flagcountry|Kingdom of Romania}}: [[Order of Carol I]], Grand Cross with Collar, ''1906''<ref>{{cite web |url=https://familiaregala.ro/ordine-si-decoratii/ordinul-carol-i |title=Ordinul Carol I |website=[[Romanian royal family|Familia Regal\u0103 a Rom\u00e2niei]] |location=Bucharest |language=ro |trans-title=Order of Carol I |access-date=17 October 2019}}</ref>\n* {{flagcountry|Russian Empire}}: \n** [[Order of St. Andrew]], Knight\n** [[Order of St. Alexander Nevsky]], Knight\n** [[Order of the White Eagle (Russia)|Imperial Order of the White Eagle]], Knight\n** [[Order of St. Anna]], Knight 1st Class\n* {{Flag|San Marino}}: [[Order of San Marino]], Grand Cross\n* {{Flagcountry|Kingdom of Sardinia|1848}}:\n** [[Supreme Order of the Most Holy Annunciation|Order of the Annunciation]], Knight, ''14 July 1855''<ref>{{Cite book|title=Notizia storica del nobilissimo ordine supremo della santissima Annunziata. Sunto degli statuti, catalogo dei cavalieri|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Q2aP6enNFoYC&dq=Ordine%20supremo%20della%20Santissima%20Annunziata&hl=en&pg=PA115#v=onepage&q&f=false|publisher=Eredi Botta|date=1869|access-date=2019-03-04|language=it|first=Luigi|surname=Cibrario|page=115}}</ref>\n** [[Order of Saints Maurice and Lazarus]], Grand Cross, ''1855''\n* {{flag|Saxe-Weimar-Eisenach}}: [[Order of the White Falcon]], Grand Cross, ''20 September 1854''<ref>''Staatshandbuch f\u00fcr das Gro\u00dfherzogtum Sachsen / Sachsen-Weimar-Eisenach'' (1855), \"Gro\u00dfherzogliche Hausorden\" [https://zs.thulb.uni-jena.de/rsc/viewer/jportal_derivate_00183881/Staatshandbuch_Film_Nr_13_0018.tif p. 12]</ref>\n* {{flagcountry|Kingdom of Saxony}}: [[Order of the Rue Crown]], Knight, ''1844''<ref>{{cite book|title=Staatshandbuch f\u00fcr den Freistaat Sachsen: 1865/66|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=SBFTAAAAcAAJ&pg=PA4|year=1866|publisher=Heinrich|page=4}}</ref>\n* {{Flagcountry|Kingdom of Serbia}}: [[Order of the Cross of Takovo]], Grand Cross\n* {{Flagicon image|Flag of Siam (1855).svg}} [[Siam]]:\n** [[Order of the Royal House of Chakri]], Knight, ''9 September 1897''<ref>{{cite journal |author=[[Royal Thai Government Gazette]] |date=14 May 1899 |url=http://www.ratchakitcha.soc.go.th/DATA/PDF/2442/007/89_4.PDF |title=\u0e1e\u0e23\u0e30\u0e23\u0e32\u0e0a\u0e17\u0e32\u0e19\u0e40\u0e04\u0e23\u0e37\u0e48\u0e2d\u0e07\u0e23\u0e32\u0e0a\u0e2d\u0e34\u0e2a\u0e23\u0e34\u0e22\u0e32\u0e20\u0e23\u0e13\u0e4c\u0e17\u0e35\u0e48\u0e1b\u0e23\u0e30\u0e40\u0e17\u0e28\u0e22\u0e38\u0e42\u0e23\u0e1b (\u0e15\u0e48\u0e2d\u0e41\u0e1c\u0e48\u0e19\u0e17\u0e35\u0e48 \u0e56 \u0e2b\u0e19\u0e49\u0e32 \u0e58\u0e53)|language=Thai |access-date=2019-05-08 }}</ref>\n** [[Order of the White Elephant]], Grand Cross\n* {{Flag|Spain|1785}}: [[Order of Charles III]], Grand Cross, ''6 April 1863''<ref>{{cite publication|url=http://hemerotecadigital.bne.es/issue.vm?id=0000941464&search=&lang=es|chapter=Real y distinguida orden de Carlos III|title=Gu\u00eda Oficial de Espa\u00f1a|last=|first=|date=1887|journal=|accessdate=21 March 2019|page=153|doi=|pmid=|language=es}}</ref>\n* {{flagicon|Sweden|1844}} {{flagicon|Norway|1844}} [[Sweden-Norway]]:\n** [[Royal Order of the Seraphim]], Knight, ''17 May 1852''<ref>{{cite book|title=Sveriges och Norges statskalender|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=9JhaAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA468|year=1874|publisher=Liberf\u00f6rlag|page=468}}</ref>\n** [[Royal Norwegian Order of St. Olav]], Grand Cross, ''13 July 1897''\n* {{flagicon|Tuscany|habsburg}} [[Grand Duchy of Tuscany|Tuscany]]:\n** [[Order of Saint Joseph|Order of St. Joseph]], Grand Cross\n** Civil and Military Order of Merit\n* {{flag|Two Sicilies}}: [[Order of Saint Ferdinand and of Merit|Order of St. Ferdinand and Merit]], Grand Cross\n* {{flagcountry|United Kingdom of Great Britain and Ireland}}: [[Order of the Garter]], Knight, ''23 February 1866''<ref name=p63>Shaw, Wm. A. (1906) ''The Knights of England'', '''I''', London, [https://archive.org/stream/cu31924092537418#page/n151/mode/2up p. 63]</ref>\n* {{Flagicon image|Flag of Venezuela (1863\u20131905).svg}} [[Venezuela]]: [[Order of the Liberator]], Grand Cross\n* {{Flag|W\u00fcrttemberg}}: [[Order of the Crown (W\u00fcrttemberg)|Order of the W\u00fcrttemberg Crown]], Grand Cross, ''1864''<ref>''[https://archive.org/details/bub_gb_Pc5CAAAAYAAJ/page/n61  Hof- und Staats-Handbuch des K\u00f6nigreich W\u00fcrttemberg]'' (1907), \"K\u00f6nigliche Orden\" p. 27</ref>\n}}\n\n===Arms===\n{| class=\"wikitable collapsible collapsed\" style=100%\n|-\n!Heraldry of Leopold II\n|-\n|\n{{Gallery|width=175|height=175|lines=3\n|File:Arms of the king of the Belgians (1837-1921).svg|Lesser coat of arms\n|File:Coat of Arms of the King of the Belgians (1837-1921).svg|Greater coat of arms as King of the Belgians\n|File:Coat of arms of the Congo Free State.svg|Greater coat of arms as Sovereign of the Congo Free State\n|File:Royal Monogram of King Leopold II, King of the Belgians.svg|Royal monogram\n}}\n|}\n\n==Ancestry==\n{{ahnentafel\n|collapsed=yes |align=center\n|boxstyle_1= background-color: #fcc;\n|boxstyle_2= background-color: #fb9;\n|boxstyle_3= backgr